SPCG Units to Acquire Up to 2.6 Billion Baht of Solar Assets

-- B y   T o n y   J o r d a n
-- 
2011-07-21T02:11:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/spcg-units-to-acquire-up-to-2-6-billion-baht-of-solar-assets.html
SPCG Pcl, a Thai operator of solar
power plants, said four of its subsidiaries will acquire up to
2.6 billion baht of “assets for the business of developing four
solar power plant projects.”  The company will seek funds from a public offering of its
shares and loans to purchase newly issued shares of the four
subsidiaries, the company said in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tony Jordan in Bangkok at 
